They have had some
encounters in the past,

00:00:55.750 --> 00:00:59.132 align:middle line:84%
I believe, actually, as recorded
in the various scriptures

00:00:59.132 --> 00:01:00.090 align:middle line:90%
from the Buddhist side.

00:01:00.090 --> 00:01:01.920 align:middle line:84%
I don't know if
in the Abrahamic--

00:01:01.920 --> 00:01:04.170 align:middle line:84%
I don't think they have any
