00:40:12.900 --> 00:40:15.660 align:middle line:84%
the direction our
science is going today--

00:40:15.660 --> 00:40:20.220 align:middle line:84%
is actually coming very close
to this Vedantic or Buddhist

00:40:20.220 --> 00:40:21.020 align:middle line:90%
perspective.

00:40:21.020 --> 00:40:21.920 align:middle line:90%
>>Absolutely.

00:40:21.920 --> 00:40:24.540 align:middle line:84%
>>Because if you look
at our technology

00:40:24.540 --> 00:40:29.010 align:middle line:84%
