00:40:38.060 --> 00:40:40.210 align:middle line:84%
And that fundamental
premise in science

00:40:40.210 --> 00:40:44.270 align:middle line:84%
is that the essential
nature of the material world

00:40:44.270 --> 00:40:47.410 align:middle line:84%
is that it's not material,
that the essential nature

00:40:47.410 --> 00:40:50.600 align:middle line:84%
of the physical world is
that it's not physical,

00:40:50.600 --> 00:40:55.210 align:middle line:84%
