what do you find?

00:41:07.270 --> 00:41:09.810 align:middle line:90%
You find an empty void.

00:41:09.810 --> 00:41:14.610 align:middle line:84%
And this empty void
is not a nothingness.

00:41:14.610 --> 00:41:15.880 align:middle line:90%
It's the womb of creation.

00:41:15.880 --> 00:41:16.790 align:middle line:90%
>>Full of energy.

00:41:16.790 --> 00:41:17.375 align:middle line:90%
>>Full of energy.

00:41:17.375 --> 00:41:18.333 align:middle line:90%
>>It's infinite energy.

00:41:18.333 --> 00:41:21.240 align:middle line:84%
>>Infinite energy and
infinite information.

00:41:21.240 --> 00:41:24.500 align:middle line:84%
