it's information that

00:41:24.500 --> 00:41:26.160 align:middle line:90%
feeds back on its own self.

00:41:26.160 --> 00:41:28.420 align:middle line:90%
It has a feedback loop.

00:41:28.420 --> 00:41:30.710 align:middle line:84%
And when information
becomes self-referral,

00:41:30.710 --> 00:41:32.650 align:middle line:90%
then it's no longer information.

00:41:32.650 --> 00:41:35.820 align:middle line:84%
