00:45:37.590 --> 00:45:40.220 align:middle line:90%
There's no dead people.

00:45:40.220 --> 00:45:42.030 align:middle line:84%
And Tibet is this
amazing culture,

00:45:42.030 --> 00:45:46.750 align:middle line:90%
which is the child of India.

00:45:46.750 --> 00:45:48.640 align:middle line:84%
It's up there on
the crown of India.

00:45:48.640 --> 00:45:50.360 align:middle line:90%
It's over the Himalaya.

00:45:50.360 --> 00:45:52.390 align:middle line:84%
And when India was
hard-pressed at the end

00:45:52.390 --> 00:45:54.720 align:middle line:84%
of the first millennium
with foreign invasions--

00:45:54.720 --> 00:45:58.560 align:middle line:84%
the first really major organized
foreign invasions into India--

00:45:58.560 --> 00:46:01.400 align:middle line:84%
then this knowledge
tradition, a lot of it

00:46:01.400 --> 00:46:04.100 align:middle line:84%
