natural liberation.

00:46:17.790 --> 00:46:24.005 align:middle line:84%
And how can we fear death when
there is only infinite life?

00:46:24.005 --> 00:46:26.130 align:middle line:84%
And when you do, the "Book
of Natural Liberation"--

00:46:26.130 --> 00:46:29.260 align:middle line:84%
which is what the real name
of the Tibetan so-called "Book

00:46:29.260 --> 00:46:31.940 align:middle line:84%
of the Dead" is-- it's the
"Book of Natural Liberation"

00:46:31.940 --> 00:46:36.730 align:middle line:84%
through learning in
the between state.

00:46:36.730 --> 00:46:39.680 align:middle line:84%
Because the minute we
die, we are totally

00:46:39.680 --> 00:46:41.160 align:middle line:90%
