describes all of reality

00:48:09.460 --> 00:48:13.330 align:middle line:84%
is a projection of which state
of consciousness you're in.

00:48:13.330 --> 00:48:15.790 align:middle line:84%
So depending on the state
of consciousness you're in,

00:48:15.790 --> 00:48:19.960 align:middle line:84%
you project a certain
kind of reality.

00:48:19.960 --> 00:48:23.600 align:middle line:84%
