00:48:39.050 --> 00:48:41.950 align:middle line:84%
which means that your
spirit is in surveillance

00:48:41.950 --> 00:48:43.650 align:middle line:90%
even in deep sleep.

00:48:43.650 --> 00:48:49.270 align:middle line:84%
And the spirit creates its own
