00:48:49.270 --> 00:48:51.350 align:middle line:84%
So everyone has
experienced that.

00:48:51.350 --> 00:48:52.980 align:middle line:90%
No need to belabor the point.

00:48:52.980 --> 00:48:56.880 align:middle line:84%
The second state of
consciousness is dreams.

00:48:56.880 --> 00:49:00.740 align:middle line:84%
Now what we have is a little
more repertoire of experience

00:49:00.740 --> 00:49:03.440 align:middle line:84%
and our brain is functioning
a little differently.

00:49:03.440 --> 00:49:07.700 align:middle line:84%
