weaved by the karmic software.

00:49:07.700 --> 00:49:12.290 align:middle line:84%
And when we are
dreaming, it's very real.

00:49:12.290 --> 00:49:17.330 align:middle line:84%
No one can convince us
that this is not real.

00:49:17.330 --> 00:49:19.800 align:middle line:84%
It's only after we wake
up that we look back

00:49:19.800 --> 00:49:24.780 align:middle line:84%
and say, oh, that was
an interesting dream.

00:49:24.780 --> 00:49:27.760 align:middle line:84%
The insight that it
was a dream happens

00:49:27.760 --> 00:49:29.750 align:middle line:84%
after you wake up
from the dream,

00:49:29.750 --> 00:49:33.110 align:middle line:84%
not in the dream-- unless
