00:49:36.540 --> 00:49:39.430 align:middle line:84%
But the insight that
that was a dream only

00:49:39.430 --> 00:49:42.051 align:middle line:84%
occurs after you wake
up from the dream.

00:49:42.051 --> 00:49:44.700 align:middle line:90%


00:49:44.700 --> 00:49:48.800 align:middle line:84%
Now Vedanta says when you
wake up from that dream,

00:49:48.800 --> 00:49:52.920 align:middle line:90%
you wake up into another dream.

00:49:52.920 --> 00:49:55.240 align:middle line:84%
And that other dream
is what you call

00:49:55.240 --> 00:49:57.720 align:middle line:90%
waking state of consciousness.

