00:50:02.140 --> 00:50:06.220 align:middle line:84%
So if you're in that waking
state of consciousness,

00:50:06.220 --> 00:50:10.510 align:middle line:84%
then you're participating
in it just like you

00:50:10.510 --> 00:50:14.760 align:middle line:84%
were participating in the
dream and you don't know

00:50:14.760 --> 00:50:17.130 align:middle line:90%
that it's equally ephemeral.

00:50:17.130 --> 00:50:19.400 align:middle line:90%
It's equally transitory.

00:50:19.400 --> 00:50:21.850 align:middle line:90%
It's equally insubstantial.

00:50:21.850 --> 00:50:24.769 align:middle line:90%
It's equally illusionary.

00:50:24.769 --> 00:50:26.560 align:middle line:84%
And therefore, of
course, you get caught up

00:50:26.560 --> 00:50:28.160 align:middle line:84%
