And that's called the sixth
state of consciousness.

00:54:22.900 --> 00:54:25.530 align:middle line:84%
And then a time comes when
the ever-present witnessing

00:54:25.530 --> 00:54:28.530 align:middle line:84%
awareness here in the
subject of perception

00:54:28.530 --> 00:54:31.470 align:middle line:84%
