asserting itself very

00:56:47.500 --> 00:56:48.790 align:middle line:90%
powerfully again in the world.

00:56:48.790 --> 00:56:50.570 align:middle line:90%
And that trend will continue.

00:56:50.570 --> 00:56:53.880 align:middle line:84%
Because there is
disillusionment in the promises

00:56:53.880 --> 00:56:55.870 align:middle line:84%
