00:57:08.335 --> 00:57:09.610 align:middle line:90%
Ha ha ha.

00:57:09.610 --> 00:57:12.790 align:middle line:84%
And people are really giving
that up on the planet.

00:57:12.790 --> 00:57:17.050 align:middle line:84%
But then if spirituality
returns in this old way

00:57:17.050 --> 00:57:19.850 align:middle line:84%
where people are
content and where

00:57:19.850 --> 00:57:23.420 align:middle line:84%
