really terrible.

00:58:31.320 --> 00:58:36.530 align:middle line:84%
The only solution is
to take our ingenuity,

00:58:36.530 --> 00:58:39.800 align:middle line:84%
to take our technologies,
to take our information age

00:58:39.800 --> 00:58:44.730 align:middle line:84%
