They can chase their
yaks around a field.

00:59:04.930 --> 00:59:06.680 align:middle line:84%
They don't have a great
deal of knowledge.

00:59:06.680 --> 00:59:08.170 align:middle line:90%
They have Bhakti.

00:59:08.170 --> 00:59:11.260 align:middle line:84%
But they have been
steeping themselves

00:59:11.260 --> 00:59:14.560 align:middle line:84%
in a culture that understands
the connection of knowledge

00:59:14.560 --> 00:59:18.250 align:middle line:84%
and love and understands that--
through their theory of karma,

00:59:18.250 --> 00:59:20.700 align:middle line:84%
of course, and reincarnation--
that we have all

00:59:20.700 --> 00:59:24.920 align:middle line:84%
been reborn infinitely--
intertwined, all of us.

00:59:24.920 --> 00:59:27.560 align:middle line:90%
We've all been lovers.

00:59:27.560 --> 00:59:28.584 align:middle line:90%
Even the guys.

00:59:28.584 --> 00:59:29.500 align:middle line:90%
We've all been lovers.

00:59:29.500 --> 00:59:31.370 align:middle line:84%
We've all been
parents and children.

00:59:31.370 --> 00:59:34.320 align:middle line:84%
We've all been enemies, too,
but we won't be mentioning that.

00:59:34.320 --> 00:59:36.810 align:middle line:84%
We've all had all different
kinds of problems,

00:59:36.810 --> 00:59:38.950 align:middle line:84%
but we've been
infinitely intertwined.

00:59:38.950 --> 00:59:42.760 align:middle line:84%
So when this kind of toothless
Tibetan today out there

00:59:42.760 --> 00:59:45.350 align:middle line:84%
with their yak, knowing
very little, looks at you,

00:59:45.350 --> 00:59:49.690 align:middle line:84%
you feel that they see
the kinship in you.

00:59:49.690 --> 00:59:51.740 align:middle line:90%
And that's all that is needed.

00:59:51.740 --> 00:59:55.740 align:middle line:84%
So that when your wild, crazy
Muslim fundamentalist looks

00:59:55.740 --> 00:59:59.730 align:middle line:84%
at your wild, crazy
Lynchburg, Virginia Protestant

00:59:59.730 --> 01:00:02.590 align:middle line:84%
