are looking at each other

01:00:02.590 --> 01:00:07.740 align:middle line:84%
with their each notion of a
triumphal nuclear-tipped god.

01:00:07.740 --> 01:00:11.210 align:middle line:84%
And yet they look beyond
that and they see kin.

01:00:11.210 --> 01:00:14.010 align:middle line:84%
They see this one guy wearing
pajamas and this other guy

01:00:14.010 --> 01:00:16.750 align:middle line:84%
wearing his little puffy
suit, that they're kin.

01:00:16.750 --> 01:00:20.560 align:middle line:90%
Then they won't kill each other.

01:00:20.560 --> 01:00:27.970 align:middle line:84%
The change in consciousness
