teaching-- three levels.

01:03:10.550 --> 01:03:12.160 align:middle line:84%
And the first level
of relativity,

01:03:12.160 --> 01:03:14.990 align:middle line:84%
which is the coarsest one,
is where Buddhism and science

01:03:14.990 --> 01:03:17.100 align:middle line:84%
completely meet but
with a different focus--

01:03:17.100 --> 01:03:20.900 align:middle line:84%
Buddhists toward the interior
as more important-- not

01:03:20.900 --> 01:03:22.010 align:middle line:90%
exclusively important.

01:03:22.010 --> 01:03:24.760 align:middle line:84%
The exterior is also important--
medicine and biology all

01:03:24.760 --> 01:03:28.620 align:middle line:84%
that is important-- but the
interior is more important.

01:03:28.620 --> 01:03:30.500 align:middle line:84%
That's cause and
effect-- causality.

01:03:30.500 --> 01:03:31.640 align:middle line:90%
And that's the first level.

01:03:31.640 --> 01:03:33.300 align:middle line:84%
And there there's
attunement, and there

01:03:33.300 --> 01:03:34.341 align:middle line:90%
can be a lot of dialogue.

01:03:34.341 --> 01:03:37.860 align:middle line:84%
The second level is the
level of part and whole

01:03:37.860 --> 01:03:40.099 align:middle line:84%
