terms of parts and wholes.

01:03:40.099 --> 01:03:41.390 align:middle line:90%
And that's a more subtle level.

01:03:41.390 --> 01:03:44.306 align:middle line:84%
And there's also, however--
with the subatomic

01:03:44.306 --> 01:03:45.930 align:middle line:84%
