01:06:59.050 --> 01:07:02.060 align:middle line:90%
infinitely interwoven.

01:07:02.060 --> 01:07:05.730 align:middle line:84%
So to make it
simple-- in grammar,

01:07:05.730 --> 01:07:09.170 align:middle line:84%
a tangled hierarchy would
be the following sentence--

01:07:09.170 --> 01:07:11.560 align:middle line:90%
I am a liar.

01:07:11.560 --> 01:07:15.100 align:middle line:84%
See, the subject qualifies the
predicate and the predicate

01:07:15.100 --> 01:07:16.140 align:middle line:90%
qualifies the subject.

01:07:16.140 --> 01:07:19.060 align:middle line:84%
If I say, I am a liar,
then if I'm lying,

01:07:19.060 --> 01:07:20.490 align:middle line:90%
I'm telling the truth.

01:07:20.490 --> 01:07:24.010 align:middle line:84%
And if I'm telling the
truth, I must be lying.

01:07:24.010 --> 01:07:26.070 align:middle line:90%
So what am I?

01:07:26.070 --> 01:07:28.080 align:middle line:90%
Am I truthful or am I a liar?

01:07:28.080 --> 01:07:30.600 align:middle line:84%
That's a tangled
hierarchy in grammar.

01:07:30.600 --> 01:07:35.490 align:middle line:84%
And you cannot get out of the
tangled hierarchy while you

01:07:35.490 --> 01:07:36.710 align:middle line:90%
stay in it.

01:07:36.710 --> 01:07:39.690 align:middle line:84%
The only way to get out
of the tangled hierarchy

01:07:39.690 --> 01:07:43.600 align:middle line:84%
is to jump out of the system--
to transcend the system.

01:07:43.600 --> 01:07:45.380 align:middle line:84%
And in this case,
in grammar, you

01:07:45.380 --> 01:07:49.320 align:middle line:84%
would say, who's making that
statement-- I am a liar?

01:07:49.320 --> 01:07:51.420 align:middle line:84%
And the one who's
making that statement

01:07:51.420 --> 01:07:54.980 align:middle line:84%
has the potential for both
lying and telling the truth.

01:07:54.980 --> 01:07:57.440 align:middle line:84%
So you understand what
a tangled hierarchy is?

01:07:57.440 --> 01:07:59.340 align:middle line:84%
Now in physics,
tangled hierarchy

01:07:59.340 --> 01:08:01.920 align:middle line:84%
says that the
subject of experience

01:08:01.920 --> 01:08:05.610 align:middle line:84%
and the object of
experience co-arise

01:08:05.610 --> 01:08:11.290 align:middle line:84%
simultaneously moment by moment
from a transcendent domain

01:08:11.290 --> 01:08:13.140 align:middle line:90%
which is beyond space and time.

01:08:13.140 --> 01:08:15.350 align:middle line:90%
And that's who you are.

01:08:15.350 --> 01:08:18.149 align:middle line:84%
You are neither the
subject nor the object

01:08:18.149 --> 01:08:21.689 align:middle line:84%
nor the process of interaction
between subject and object,

01:08:21.689 --> 01:08:23.883 align:middle line:84%
but the potential
for the whole thing--

01:08:23.883 --> 01:08:27.430 align:middle line:84%
for the subject, the object,
and the process of interaction.

01:08:27.430 --> 01:08:30.330 align:middle line:84%
This is very Vedantic
